r /><strong>1.&#39;岩石&#39;N&#39;Roll Star&#39;（Monnow Valley版本）</strong><br /> <strong>2.“ Shakermaker”（Monnow Valley版本）</strong><br /> <strong>3.“永远活着”（Monnow Valley版本）</strong><br /> <strong>4.“在天空中”（Monnow Valley版本）</strong><br /> <strong>5.“哥伦比亚”（Monnow Valley版本）</strong><br /> <strong>6.“放下它”（Monnow Valley版本）</strong><br /> <strong>7.“香烟和酒精”（Monnow Valley版本）</strong><br /> <strong>8.“ Digsy的晚餐”（Monnow Valley版本）</strong><br /> <strong>9.&#39;岩石&#39;n&#39;Roll Star&#39;（Sawmills Outtake）</strong><br /> <strong>10.“在天空中”（锯木厂的出现）</strong><br /> <strong>11.&#39;哥伦比亚&#39;（锯木厂的餐厅）</strong><br /> <strong>12.“放下它”（锯木厂的出现）</strong><br /> <strong>13.“香烟和酒精”（锯木厂的出现）</strong><br /> <strong>14.“ Digsy的晚餐”（Sawmills Outtake）</strong><br /> <strong>15.“滑动”（锯木厂的出现）</strong><br /> <strong>16.“悲伤的歌”（Mauldeth Road West Demo，11月92日）</strong> </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="诺埃尔·加拉格尔（Noel Gallagher" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/qUl5BVqtNZU?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/reunion-or-reissue-fans-are-getting-excited-by-the-new-oasis-teaser-3758069">乐队本周在网上嘲笑了即将到来的重新发行</a>，导致一些歌迷相信重聚正在卡上。去年， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-confirms-definitely-maybe-30th-anniversary-reissue-for-2024-denies-oasis-reunion-tour-3436441">诺埃尔（Noel）确认，“绝对也许”将于2024年到来，</a>以庆祝其三十年的里程碑。</p><p>同时，他疏远的兄弟和前队友利亚姆（Liam <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-oasis-definitely-maybe-30th-anniversary-uk-tour-dates-tickets-3515369">）将于下个月进行特别的“也许”英国和爱尔兰巡回演出</a>。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-to-play-oasis-definitely-maybe-in-full-at-reading-leeds-2024-3548140#:~:text=Reading%20%26%20Leeds%202024-,Liam%20Gallagher%20to%20play%20Oasis'%20'Definitely%20Maybe'%20in,full%20at%20Reading%20%26%20Leeds%20202